This paper deals with multilingual knowledge graph embeddings, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves the use of embeddings, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with knowledge graphs, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and databases (cs.DB).
